---
title: Mushroom Quesadillas with Lemony Guacamole
description: This fiesta of flavors will satisfy your craving for Mexican, plus it's vegetarian, so everyone can enjoy! WE added a squeeze of lemon and some lemon zest to the guacamole to brighten it - feel free to add more or less, depending on how much zing you're looking for!
